{"word":"H5660 - עַבְדִּי - ʻAbdîy - ab-dee' - Abdi","slug":"H5660","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עַבְדִּי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻAbdîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ab-dee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abdi"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עבדּי</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛abdı̂y</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ab-dee'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Abdi = \"servant of Jehovah\" <ol><li>a Merarite Levite and ancestor of Ethan the singer</li><li>a Merarite Levite, father of Kish, in the time of king Hezekiah of Judah</li><li>one of the family of Elam who had a foreign wife in the time of Ezra</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H5647\">H5647</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4566\">H4566</a>, <a href=\"#/H5647\">H5647</a>, <a href=\"#/H5650\">H5650</a>, <a href=\"#/H5651\">H5651</a>, <a href=\"#/H5652\">H5652</a>, <a href=\"#/H5653\">H5653</a>, <a href=\"#/H5654\">H5654</a>, <a href=\"#/H5655\">H5655</a>, <a href=\"#/H5656\">H5656</a>, <a href=\"#/H5657\">H5657</a>, <a href=\"#/H5658\">H5658</a>, <a href=\"#/H5659\">H5659</a>, <a href=\"#/H5661\">H5661</a>, <a href=\"#/H5662\">H5662</a>, <a href=\"#/H5663\">H5663</a>, <a href=\"#/H5664\">H5664</a>, <a href=\"#/H5744\">H5744</a>"}]}